content:
Give agents access to Einstein Knowledge Creation by assigning them a permission set. This is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on.

To assign permission sets: Assign Permission Sets AND View Setup and Configuration.

Select the agents you want to use Knowledge Creation.
Drafting with Einstein cuts down on effort but can't replace your agents. Create an approval process to review generated articles by experts before publishing.
Assign selected agents the Einstein Knowledge Creation permission set, included with the Einstein for Service add-on.
title: Giving Agents Access to Einstein Knowledge Creation in Service Cloud
